{"tid":684201,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"E家d小學雞超有錢","createTime":"2018-05-30T10:42:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T11:29:05.000Z","uid":160539,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5b4b6618ea1ad63d364da8e6772541ab2a366e37","tid":684201,"uid":160539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"岩岩買野飲既時候，條隊有兩個小學雞排緊，突然有一個肥仔（小學雞）行去佢地中間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：肥仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：小學雞1 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：小學雞2<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你揀佢定揀我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我兩個都揀<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：唔得你要兩之中揀一個<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：咁我兩個都唔揀<br />\n個肥仔就一直係咁問，小學雞1都一直唔出聲，另一個鍾於頂唔順<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你唔好煩佢啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：香港有言論自由<br />\n條肥仔就開始說服小學雞1<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我每日都有比20蚊你，又請你食野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：（都係一直唔出聲）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：佢淨係識同你傾計<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：你淨係識用錢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：係呀我有錢大曬，吹呀死乞兒<br />\n呢個時候，我就走左趕住番學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想唔到e家d小學雞係咁樣識朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb83998698d7303db80abce6ef125ce4e6b0c7c8","tid":684201,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T10:43:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b16